## 8HOUR.md Update Discipline

After completing any module workflow, you MUST update `8HOUR.md` using `lib/8hour-lead/8hour-md-updater.ts`:

1. `replaceSection` for sections the module owns (e.g., adr â†’ architecture-decisions)
2. `appendToSection` for the decision-log entry
3. `stampFrontmatter` with `updated_by: "/8hour-lead <module>"` and the current `8hour_lead_version`
4. Run `{{BIN_ROOT}}/8hour-lead-validate` to check the result is well-formed

If `8HOUR.md` exceeds the configured `max_lines` (default 400), rotate the oldest half of the Decision Log entries into `docs/8hour/decisions/archive.md`.

